Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' before moving to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Difference in average time between 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average time it takes to resolve a case after 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Total time cases spend in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' compared to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Maximum time cases remain in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' before any next activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000002583FC292D0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average time between 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the next activity in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Average delay time added by 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in the process flow
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Closed' in cases with high impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Difference in average resolution time between cases with 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and cases with 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average time cases are in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' when followed by 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + In Call' across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
